{"type": "article", "id": 14111, "title": "世界上第一款“卷轴”的键盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-28T07:27:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 113, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021255039PftVK34UIJWwkLR.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLG 最近推出了世界上第一款“卷轴”的键盘，把“便携”发挥到了极致。键盘采用卷轴式设计，卷起来后可以轻轻松松塞进包里，而摊平以后则是一个结实的键盘，通过蓝牙 3.0 可以和智能手机，平板电脑连接，而且可以同时连接两台设备。键盘依靠 AAA 电池供电，续航能力达到 3 个月。这款产品将会在下个月率先在美国面市。<a href=\"http://www.lg.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141726qKISXjkO3V6rCQZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141727D58jJUp9zsYP63SA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614172835f4W7J2mgCbuUHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141728f6m4EHVyINlUpzsC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141728DJTWZfb6pyK3hadC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}